Imi tețbeggin-ed belli d iqeddacen n Sidi Ṛebbi i nella deg wayen akk nxeddem : nṣebbeṛ i teswiɛin n ceddat, i lḥif, i tugdi, iwakken ur țɣawal ara aț-țesseṛḥiben ara lqima i wayen yellan deg-s.
uqbel a d-yedṛu wannect-a, kunwi s inelmaden-iw a d-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ yeɛnan wid i yi-d-yernan ɣer webrid, axaṭer ilaq ad yethedden wul-iw.
A nezger (2006), ixebbeṛ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-yefk Sidi Ṛebbi tazmert i wid ara t-iɛiwnen seg wayen sɛan d zzyada, s wakka ihi aț-țemɛadalem,
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ara nexdem iwakken ur qebblen ara ayen s wayes ara tedṛu d uquṛan ; lameɛna m'ara t-neḥmed a t-walin iwakken ad acḥal ilaq ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
ilaq ad yeṭṭef deg awal n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan ț-țideț akken i t-yelmed, yerna ad yizmir ad isselmed, ad inhu wiyaḍ yerna a d-isbeggen i wid i d-yekkaten deg awal-agi, belli ɣelṭen.
Di lweqt-nni, kra n yemdanen usan-d a d-ḥeṛṛu s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, eɛni ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, qebblen-t iwakken a d-nbeggen acḥal nebɣa a nɛiwen-iten.
Imi ibabaten-nneɣ i ɣ-d-isɛan țțaken-aɣ tiyita yerna nqudeṛ-iten, amek ur nețqadaṛ ara Ṛebbi yellan d ajdid.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen, iwakken a nili di lefhama.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tiseḍwa-agi, acḥal yewɛeṛ : yewɛeṛ ccan sennig lɛulama n ccariɛa yellan di tazwara, yellan ț-țamusni i ɣef d-yesseɣlin deg yiman-nsen, lameɛna nețța isselmad-iten d ixemmimen yelhan akk-d ixemmimen n diri akk-d lefhama-nsen.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Ɣef wayen yeɛnan ajmaɛ n tikciwin i sen-yehwa, ț-țɣuṛṛit, zemren ad kksen lḥeṛma d lḥeqq, d ṣṣfa n wul, wid izemren ad ssexdamen tibṛatin i lewṣaya.
A sen-tiniḍ annect-agi iwakken a d-tessakiḍ deg waṭas n lecɣal nwen, ad sɛun ayen ara ḥwiǧen, yerna ad fken amur di lɣella nsen deg ubrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Di mkul amkan nesla yedṛa leḥṛam d ameqqran gar-asen. A Sidi, acḥal kan i glaq aț-țenṭaṛṛem iwakken aț-țerrem ddehn-is ɣer wemkan-is ɣuṛ-sen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wujeṛṛeb ( taɛekkumt) amextaf n tɣuṛaft-agi yellan di tmurt, ara yilin d uselmed n wid iḥekkmen ɣef yiman-nsen.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yeẓẓa tafeṛṛant am akken teqbeṛt leḥḥun, tețnerni deg webrid n leslak akk-d lemqamat n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ. Mmugren-d iferrawen, imiren mkul aseggas țwaxedṣen s wayen sɛan d zzyada.
Di tejmaɛt n temdint n Ludikus ad afen deg-s lɣaci. Ma ț-țilawin yumnen s Lmasiḥ, mkul yiwen seg-sen ad ččen d wid imeɛnen yerna ad ssiwḍen lexbaṛ i inelmaden.
Inelmaden n temdint n Antyuc, msefhamen belli mkul yiwen deg-sen a d-yefk ayen iwumi yezmer, iwakken ad ɛiwnen atmaten izedɣen di temdint n Lud, iwakken ad ɣleb ṭṭwabeɛ-ines.
Di teswiɛt-nni kan, lɣaci yennejmaɛ-ed s luluf armi țemyeɛfasen. Ilaq ad xedmen ccɣel i inelmaden-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel akk-d uselmed n tideț.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut lbaḍna n Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad țekkin di tdukklisen, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin lweqt di leqsed. M'ara ɛeddin lweqt-nni ɣer uselmed-ines di Lmasiḥ, ad innekmal.
