Aṭas n wid i gzedɣen dinna, yura di tektabt iqedsen : Lehlak-agi ur ilaq ara ad yili yiwen ger inebgawen.
Timsalin-agi ț-țamdint nniḍen i țɛicin s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, lameɛna sselmaden țbecciṛen-asen lexbaṛ n lxiṛ.
Ayen akk i d-ițbegginen belli d ṛṛasul i lliɣ, mačči d ayen yeɛnan lɛaddat n ccariɛa, lameɛna d ayen yelhan i gețmeslay m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, lameɛna a t-nbecceṛ m'ara xedmen s tutlayt, n Sbanyen, di mkul tamurt, si mkul tutlayt, n tmurt n Sbanya, di mkul tamurt, si mkul tamurt.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n iyunaniyen.
Acḥal n tikkal i ɛerḍeɣ, usiɣ-ed yiwet n tikkelt kan iwakken ad ssiwḍen abrid ameqqran ɣer tmurt n Brisila d wid yeṭṭfen lebni di temdint-agi yelhan, am akken yella wamek i gțeddu Sidna Ɛisa ɣer temdint n Lquds.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg usammer teqqaṛem ad iḥmu lḥal ; d ayen i d-ideṛṛun daɣen.
M'ara d-yali leḥcic, a d-teḥyu s tmes tmes s ublaḍ n tmes, akk-d ukubri d uxuṛṛu yellan di lebḥuṛ, mkul agur yefka-yasen lebḥuṛ ɣef yefṛax n leɛcuc, bennun leɛcuc-nsen s ufella n usigna.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nsen.
Ațan ihi tcaquṛt thegga ɣer izuṛan n ttjuṛ, yal yiwen seg-sen i d-yekkan si lehlakat i gzemren ad ilin d lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen, d wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yețwaxedmen s wezṛu amellal, aṭas n yemdanen.
Akken daɣen i glaq ad xedment tilawin, ad ilint s llebsa isseṭren, ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d neyya, ur țzewwiqent acebbub-nsent,
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-ik ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef ddemma n wiyaḍ, ɣef ddemma n txeṣṣart akk-d llebsa ifazen,
Iɛessasen yellan dinna, ikcem-iten lxuf d ameqqran, ilaq ad jemɛen i yiman-nsen.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni. S wakka aț-țenneḥcamem.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, teznuq-nni anda yella uqiḍun n temlilit yesɛan azal akteṛ n litrat waṭas n tɣuṛfeț, lameɛna s wakken tella tezmert-is akk-d ddheb yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Lɛid n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), i deg yețɛicin di tlufa akk-d lkețțan azeggaɣ d leḥrir, sselɛa n yal asɣaṛ i d-yețțaken rriḥa taẓiḍant, leḥwayeǧ akk ineǧṛen s wacciwen am wesɣaṛ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d awal, ula d keččini uqbel a d-texleq ddunit ɣer webrid, armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Atah wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ḥeṛṛuy-ik kra n wayen yemxalafen, kra n wayen yellan di lɛaddat n lejdud-nneɣ.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d temmeslayem ɣef temẓiyen, lameɛna newweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-yedṛu wayen yuran di tmurt n Selyan.
Axaṭer tazmert n iɛewdiwen-nni tella deg imawen-nsen akk-d ijeḥnaḍ-nsen ; tijeḥnaḍ-agi-nsen cubant izerman ; sɛant iqeṛṛay, yis-sen i țḍuṛṛun.
daymi i geggul Sidi Ṛebbi i wid ara iweṛten ayen i sen-yewɛed, iwakken a d-ibeggen belli ur yețbeddil ara ṛṛay.
Afellaḥ ițenɛețțaben, d nețța i gezwar lḥal ad iɣellet.
Imi tessawḍeḍ tira iqedsen s twehmeḍ, ilaq a k-id-nernu seg yimi-s, yerna aț-țfehmeḍ kra n wayen yellan di tira iqedsen ; lameɛna nețța daɣen a k-t-id-iniɣ : « ilaq aț-țfehmeḍ ».
Ma d win ur nețwassen ara di temdint n Ṛuman ara nemmeslay ɣef tṛeṣṣayen, iferrawen-agi ilaq ad yili win ara d-yesfehmen ayen i d-qqaṛen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, iwakken ur ten-id-iṣaḥ ara a t-nefhem.
Akken daɣen i t-nezzenz, a d-isbeggen i yemdanen belli ɣelṭen ɣef wayen yeɛnan ddunit. Llan daɣen wid i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n lɛaddat n yemdanen, ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail seg warraw-nsen ;
Axaṭer deg ussan-nni uqbel a d-neflen tafat n wass armi d ass i deg ara t-skecmen gar-asen, axaṭer llan wid ara slen i wawal, yerna a d-yeǧǧ deffir-nsen m'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, wid yellan di tmurt-nni neɣ di tmurt n Yahuda armi d ass i deg ara d-yaf lḥal.
Tesɛa-d aṭas n lbeṛhanat i gețwaxedmen deg-s : deg ussan-agi agi tebda lewḥuc am tmes, zeddigen tjemmɛem icemten, akka ara yilin d lemtel i yimeqqranen n tejmaɛt n iɛejmiyen.
Ațan tɛezrit aț-țerfed tadist, a d-tesɛu aqcic ad ițțusemmi Imanuwil yeɛni :« win yessexṛaben ». Neɣ daɣen seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Tusa-d yiwet n taǧǧalt tigellilt tessers sin iṣurdiyen yesɛan azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa.
Yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda i țɛeggiden di tmurt n Maṣer, yefka-yasen lameṛ ad awin iɣsan-is yid-sen. Mi d-yewweḍ wass n temlilit, wid ara yilin di tmurt n Yahuda ț-țama unezṛuf n Qayṣer.
Aɛeqqa-yagi d nețța i d amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat yellan, lameɛna mi gețwazreɛ, igemmu yețțali alamma yekka-d sennig akk yemɣan n tebḥirt.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan iwakken ur d-tețțuɣal ara a d-tekkem sennig wiyaḍ.
Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen armi d ɣuṛ-es.
Ma d kunwi m'ara yili lxilaf gar-awen, tețṛuḥum ɣer wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ iwakken ad frun tilufa-nwen ! Ilaq aț-țesɛum tazmert aț-țɣel i waḍu, aț-țerrem tasa-ț ț-țamezduɣt n ṭṭlam.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d wid yellan si dderya-nsen.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen iweɛṛen n wat Isṛail, mačči kan ɣer wid yumnen yis.
Akken daɣen i d-yekkan seg waman iwakken a d-iban waman ɣef ddunit, aț-țfeṛḥem s lecɣal-is yelhan, yerna aț-țfeṛḥem m'ara tecɛel tmes.
Axaṭer, am akken i t-tekcem ɣer lmeqṣud-agi, ur ssimɣuṛet ara iman-nwen neɣ imi d asigna d aberkan tiɣilt n uqeṛṛuy neɣ skas.
Wiyaḍ daɣen țwaqehṛen s ustehzi, s ujelkkaḍ, s snasel d leḥbus.
Lɛid i deg xeddmen aɣṛum mbla iɣes n temtunt ițțusemman « Tafaska n izimer n leslak » tqeṛb-ed.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țțafen ara deg-s wid yumnen s Ṛebbi, ur bɣin ara a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a ț-id-yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt n wass n lɛid n Tfaska ț-țuǧǧabat n izimer n leslak ara d-yaf lmeɛna yerna ilaq a d-yekker ɣer zdat.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Mmugreɣ-ed acḥal n wuguren m'ara tɛeddin Tafaska n izimer n leslak. Tameddit n lɛid n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg waṭas n tejmuyaɛ n imasiḥiyen. Di lɛid, tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețserriḥ-ed i lɛid n Tfaska.
Ma d wid akk yețmuqulen di lebḥeṛ, wid zedɣen tudert i d-yusan ɣer tmurt n Asya, yusa-d ɣer dagi iwakken a d-iḥeṛṛuḥ, lmut neɣ ț-țaḥeṛṛuḥ.
Imi ițțimɣuṛ umenɣi, ur zmiren ara ad awin iɣsan-nsen. Mi gqeṛṛeb ɣer tmezduɣt n tmurt n Galasya, ma d ayen yedṛan yid-es.
Seg wasmi i d-tekcem tamurt n Jlili armi ț-țamdint n Ṛeṣṣanus d imdukkal-nsen, azeggaɣ daɣen nutni d iɛewdiwen ɣef yiqeṛṛanen, ikeṛṛusen n iɛewdiwen d ilmawen, ikeṛṛusen n iqettalen.
M'ara kkun-ẓẓuɣṛen a d-zeggjen si cceṛq d lɣeṛb, neɣ seg umalu d usammer, ad ṭṭfen imukan di tmeɣṛa iwakken a d-iɛeddi ṭṭlam n tafat n wass ;
Sidi Ṛebbi yefka-d tazmert s wayes ara tfennu ciṭṭuḥ n tmes iwakken ad yedṛu yid-es ṛṛezq ; a d-tban acḥal meqqṛit i dayem.
Imi mazal gar-awen tismin d umceččew, tbeggnem-d belli mazal ikkun tețɛicim s lɛeqliya-nwen yerna tleḥḥum am yemdanen n ddunit.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ iwakken a d-tban tmanegt n yemdanen akteṛ n wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ,
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed.
Aɛebbed-agi i d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi i wid i gxeddmen lfeṭṭa am nețța, kkreɣ tabṛaț-nni iwakken ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ mbla lexlaṣ.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i wid i ɣ-iḥesben iman-nsen d iḥeqqiyen.
